                    <span>Refreshingly different. For those seeking something less than the number crunching books but more than just another history lesson, Baseball and Philosophy delivers providing the serious fan with a series of short essays aimed at America's baseball institution. Taken from our (www.baseball-almanac.com) full review done February 28, 2004).</span>
                  
              
